    - rid: 4538204687926035310
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Good morning, sir! I found your ad saying you're looking for an employee?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204687926035311
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Welcome, my name is Rolf. Yes, I'm looking for someone who has some
          muscles... Have you ever worked on farm?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204687926035312
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Yes, I was born on farm.
    - rid: 4538204687926035313
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: No, but I'm not afraid. I am fast learner.
    - rid: 4538204687926035314
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Great, I just need someone to pick up the turnips and corn from my
          field. I can't do it anymore, and those damn weeds that are just waiting
          to bite you. Can you do this?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204687926035315
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Of course, I can help you.
    - rid: 4538204687926035316
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Well, I think it's not for me. Maybe later.
    - rid: 4538204687926035317
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Oh okay. I will wait here if you change your mind.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204687926035318
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: So, can you help me with harvest?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204687926035319
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: 'Good, take this key, open the gate and pick up corn and turnip from
          the field. Then come to me, bring me this and I will give you reward.  '
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204687926035320
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I need 10 cobs of corn and 10 turnips.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204687926035321
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Do you have my crops?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
